nodes.bodyText:
This is nifty. I might need a little more detail in the comments (especially if my reflection is rusty).
Thinking out loud, I wonder if you could refactor the Enums classes such that each matching pair of to & from methods just has the same name across the board. E.g. they could all inherit from something like
interface EnumMappable<T extends Enum<T>> {
  T toEnum(Short short);
  short toStorage(T enum);
}

